See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EnvironmentFunctions
    Functions used to access the system environment.
    PropertiesFunctions

    PropertyInjectionExtension
    A CDI extension that supports injection of properties (e.g.
    PropertyInjectionPointWrapper
    A wrapper for an InjectionPoint that will be injected with a property value.
    PropertyLiteral

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoSuchConverterException
    An exception thrown when a converter named on a Property qualifier cannot be found.
    UnresolvedExpressionException
    An exception thrown when an expression evaluates to a null value.
    UnresolvedPropertyException
    An exception thrown when a named property cannot be resolved to a value.
    UnsupportedTypeException
    An exception thrown when the target type for a property injection has no associated converter.
